item.title: Labor market added 911,000 fewer jobs than earlier reported, BLS says
item.description: The downward revision from the Bureau of Labor Statistics shows the job market was slowing in 2024 and early 2025.

item.title: Israel says it carried out strike targeting Hamas leaders as explosions rock Doha, Qatar
item.description: Israel says it carried out a strike targeting Hamas leaders. One Israeli official says it happened in Doha, Qatar. CBS News' Ramy Inocencio reports.

item.title: School bus carrying Oklahoma softball team crashes, injuring 8
item.description: A school bus carrying an Oklahoma City-area softball team crashed Monday evening, injuring eight people, officials said.

item.title: Russian strike kills at least 20 in east Ukraine, Zelenskyy says
